query:
SELECT id, strategySymbol, status, isTest, ipAddress, createdAt, errorMessage,
       SUBSTRING(payload, 1, 300) as payload_preview
FROM webhook_logs 
WHERE ipAddress NOT IN ('test-simulator', '::1', '127.0.0.1', 'localhost', '')
AND ipAddress IS NOT NULL
AND DATE(createdAt) >= DATE_SUB(CURDATE(), INTERVAL 7 DAY)
ORDER BY createdAt DESC
LIMIT 30;
